ince’; a byname of the beautiful youth Skanda, son of Shiva."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Juhel Molis (2 Sons) was born in 1140, in Exbourne, Devon, England, his father, Nicholas de Molis, was 31 and his mother, Mrs. Nicholas De Moels, was 24. He married Lady Emma Exbourne Baldwin de Molis in 1168, in Exbourne, Devon, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1166, in England, United Kingdom, at the age of 26, and was buried in England."},"et":{"1140–1166":"1140–1166","1147–1170":"1147–1170","1146–Female":"1146–Surnud","1165–1227":"1165–1227","1110–1173":"1110–1173","1116–Female":"1116–Surnud","1190":"1190","1110":"1110","1165":"1165","1140":"1140","1173":"1173","1170":"1170","1227":"1227","1116":"1116","1137":"1137","1147":"1147","1146":"1146","Abt 1165":"umbes 1165","1166":"1166","Exbourne, Devon, England":"Exbourne, Devon, England","England":"England","Devon, England":"Devon, England","Devon, Devonshire, England":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1140–1166":"1140–1166","1147–1170":"1147–1170","1146–Female":"1146–Kuollut","1165–1227":"1165–1227","1110–1173":"1110–1173","1116–Female":"1116–Kuollut","1190":"1190","1110":"1110","1165":"1165","1140":"1140","1173":"1173","1170":"1170","1227":"1227","1116":"1116","1137":"1137","1147":"1147","1146":"1146","Abt 1165":"noin 1165","1166":"1166","Exbourne, Devon, England":"Exbourne, Devon, England","England":"England","Devon, England":"Devon, England","Devon, Devonshire, England":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1140–1166":"1140–1166","1147–1170":"1147–1170","1146–Female":"1146–Décédée","1165–1227":"1165–1227","1110–1173":"1110–1173","1116–Female":"1116–Décédée","1190":"1190","1110":"1110","1165":"1165","1140":"1140","1173":"1173","1170":"1170","1227":"1227","1116":"1116","1137":"1137","1147":"1147","1146":"1146","Abt 1165":"environ 1165","1166":"1166","Exbourne, Devon, England":"Exbourne, Devon, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","Devon, England":"Devon, Angleterre","Devon, Devonshire, England":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Juhel Molis (2 Sons) est né en 1140, à Exbourne, Devon, Angleterre, son père, Nicholas de Molis, avait 31 ans et sa mère, Mrs. Nicholas De Moels, avait 24 ans. Il a épousé Lady Emma Exbourne Baldwin de Molis en 1168, à Exbourne, Devon, Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1166, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 26 ans, et a été enterré à Angleterre."},"de":{"1140–1166":"1140–1166","1147–1170":"1147–1170","1146–Female":"1146–Verstorben","1165–1227":"1165–1227","1110–1173":"1110–1173","1116–Female":"1116–Verstorben","1190":"1190","1110":"1110","1165":"1165","1140":"1140","1173":"1173","1170":"1170","1227":"1227","1116":"1116","1137":"1137","1147":"1147","1146":"1146","Abt 1165":"um 1165","1166":"1166","Exbourne, Devon, England":"Exbourne, Devon, England","England":"England","Devon, England":"Devon, England","Devon, Devonshire, England":"Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Als Juhel Molis (2 Sons) 1140 in Exbourne, Devon, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater Nicholas de Molis 31 und seine Mutter Mrs. Nicholas De Moels 24. Er hat 1168 in Exbourne, Devon, England Lady Emma Exbourne Baldwin de Molis geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1166 im Alter von 26 Jahren in England, United Kingdom und wurde in England begraben."},"ht":{"1140–1166":"1140–1166","1147–1170":"1147–1170","1146–Female":"1146–Desede","1165–1227":"1165–1227","1110–1173":"1110–1173","1116–Female":"1116–Desede","1190":"1190","1110":"1110","1165":"1165","1140":"1140","1173":"1173","1170":"1170","1227":"1227","1116":"1116","1137":"1137","1147":"1147","1146":"1146","Abt 1165":"about 1165","1166":"1166","Exbourne, Devon, England":"Exbourne, Devon, England","England":"England","Devon, England":"Devon, England","Devon, Devonshire, England":"Devon, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1140–1166":"1140–1166","1147–1170":"1147–1170","1146–Female":"1146–elhunyt","1165–1227":"1165–1227","1110–1173":"11